{"name":"Demon Lion","size":"large","type":"beast","tag":"Posessed","alignment":"Chaotic Evil","hitDice":"7","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"12","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"40","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"37 (5d10 + 10)","speedDesc":"40 ft.","strPoints":"17","dexPoints":"15","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"3","wisPoints":"12","chaPoints":"8","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"2","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"The tiger can take 1 Villain action on each turn:","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the tiger can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the tiger can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The tiger can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the tiger's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the tiger's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the tiger dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Keen Smell","desc":"The tiger has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on smell."},{"name":"Stalk","desc":"If the demon lion succeeds a stealth skill challenge before it is noticed, it gets a surprise round."},{"name":"Twilight Hunter","desc":"In the dusk or dawn the demon lion has advantage on stealth checks."},{"name":"Assasin","desc":"The demon lion has advantage on attacks against any surprised creature."},{"name":"Pounce","desc":"If the tiger moves at least 20 ft. straight toward a creature and then hits it with a claw attack on the same turn, that target must succeed on a DC 15 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The demon lion makes one attack with it's bite and one with it's claw, or two with it's tail spines."},{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 8 (1d10 + 3) piercing damage. The target also has to make a DC 14 Wisdom save or be frightened until the Demon Lion's next turn."},{"name":"Claw","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 7 (1d8 + 3) slashing damage."},{"name":"Tailspine","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, range 15/60 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 4 (1d4 + 2) piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Opportunist","desc":"The demon lion can make a claw attack at an adjacent enemy if they're prone."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Phase","desc":"Upon taking damage the lion goes translucent. The next two attacks against the lion have disadvantage."}],"legendaries":[{"name":"Circle","desc":"Round 1: The demon lion moves it's speed, this movement does not provoke opportunity attacks"},{"name":"Rattle","desc":"Round 2: Every creature within 30 ft must make a DC 12 wisdom save or be deafened for for a minute, or until it makes a DC 10 constitution save."},{"name":"Shadespines","desc":"Round 3: Every creature within a 40 ft cone must make a DC 13 dexterity save or take 5 (2d6) piercing damage and have their speed reduced by 10ft for a minute."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"bludgeoning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"psychic","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}